Name: SMF30UPO
Description: Product owner or vendor name (specified on the PRODOWNER option of the IFAUSAGE macro).

Name: SMF30UPN
Description: Product name (specified on the PRODNAME option of the IFAUSAGE macro).

Name: SMF30UPV
Description: Product version (if specified on the PRODVERS option of the IFAUSAGE macro or ‘NONE’).

Name: SMF30UPQ
Description: Product qualifier (if specified on the PRODQUAL option of the IFAUSAGE macro or ‘NONE’).

Name: SMF30UPI
Description: Product ID (if specified on the PRODID option of the IFAUSAGE macro or ‘NONE’).

Name: SMF30UCT
Description: Product TCB Time (in hundredths of a second).

Name: SMF30UCS
Description: Product SRB Time (in hundredths of a second).

Name: SMF30URD
Description: Product specific resource data (specified on the DATA option on the IFAUSAGE macro FUNCTIONDATA request). SMF30UDF identifies the format of the data in this field.

Name: SMF30UDF
Description: Data format of value in SMF30URD
